status_updates.description:
The main focus areas of AppCoins in the last weeks have been:

-Making our payments more user-friendly in landscape mode; 
-Tweaking our APK Migrator Tool to enable automatic migration of the billing system; 
-Improving our AppCoins Wallet’s user interface, UX and creating an additional feature for OEMs.

For further information regarding new updates and features read ANU#35: https://medium.com/@appcoins/anu-35-payments-in-landscape-wallet-updates-and-unite-shanghai-890893a0f6dc

Following AppCoins roadmap schedule, we have just launched the Kernigham Release which comes with three new features:

- An easy way to transfer AppCoins Credits among peers;
- A new Top-Up feature;
- An option to have someone else help out with a purchase.

Read more about how these new features allow AppCoins to provide an even greater circular economy: https://medium.com/@appcoins/kernigham-release-new-top-up-and-ask-someone-to-pay-features-b8ff5f2bfcc5
